I_{{n}} \left( \alpha \right) =\int _{-1/2\,\pi }^{1/2\,\pi }\!  \left( \alpha+\sin \left( x \right)  \right) ^{n} \left( \cos \left(  x \right)  \right) ^{2}{dx}
